Subject: NEA - CU-Upgrade
Description: The customer needs assistance to upgrade to the latest version of NEA
What_We_Know__c: The customer had some issues with SharePoint and was advised to upgrade to the latest version of NEA.
Solution_Comment__c:
I upgraded the NEA application from 11.6.0.125 to 11.6.0.138.
We also upgraded the Access Information Center and Sensitive Data Addon to the latest version.
